Feature: Silencio (Silencing Charm)

    Silences something immediately

    Pronunciation:
        /sɪˈlɛnsi.oʊ/ si-LEN-see-oh
    Seen/mentioned:
        First used by Hermione in Order of the Phoenix to silence a frog and a
        raven in Charms class, then later to silence a Death Eater who was
        trying to use a spell against Harry Potter. It was also used by
        Voldemort in Deathly Hallows during the Battle of Hogwarts.
